CatDescriptText: Related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 13, 1959, pg. A16 reads: "Guest Model - Alberta Thompson, another guest model for the D.I.'s shows a lounging outfit featuring knit trousers and a print top."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Alberta Thompson wearing dark pants, belt, and floral button down shirt with flipped up collar and three quarter length sleeves, barefoot, posed lying on back on pillows in Gloria Grate's house, preparing for the D.I.'s "Atlantic City U.S.A." revue held in the Press Room of the Hotel Sherwyn
